node.text: Testing buildings to see if they can withstand an Earthquake 🏠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on July 22, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, sky and text that says 'News UAE says rainstorms were created using its cloud seeding drones'.

node.text: After literally melting in the 120 degrees Fahrenheit heat, the UAE decided to seed its own rain clouds by launching drones, which then zapped clouds with electricity. They then jolted droplets in the clouds and caused them to clump together, creating rain.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on July 22, 2021. May be an image of chess, outdoors and text that says 'UNILAD TECH A YouTube live chat about chess got flagged for hate speech'.

node.text: AI is used to analyse the language used on YouTube. However, the AI doesn't understand the context with words such as "white", "black" and "attack" being completely misinterpreted.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on July 22, 2021. May be an image of body of water and text that says 'UNILAD TECH Viruses found in 15,000-year-old Tibetan glacier ice are like nothing seen before'.

node.text: Researchers found the genetic codes of 33 viruses – only four of which were previously known to us.The viruses found so far probably can't infect humans, let alone threaten our health, but we don't yet know what else is lurking there 🦠

node.text: According to new astrophysics research, our universe may not be expanding outward in all directions. Instead, it may be rolled around itself like a gigantic cosmic donut. 🍩🌌
